<h1><code ng:non-bindable="">jqmPanelContainer</code>
<div><span class="hint">directive in module <code ng:non-bindable="">jqm</code>
</span>
</div>
</h1>
<div><h2 id="description">Description</h2>
<div class="description"><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpanelcontainer-page"><p>A container for jquery mobile panels.</p>
<p>If you wish to use this with a view, you want the jqm-panel-container as the
parent of your view and your panels. For example:
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
&lt;div jqm-panel-container="myPanel"&gt;
  &lt;div jqm-panel&gt;My Panel!&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div jqm-view&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
</div></div>
<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>
<div class="usage">as attribute<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&lt;ANY jqm-panel-container="{expression}"&gt;
   ...
&lt;/ANY&gt;</pre>
<h4 id="usage_parameters">Parameters</h4><table class="variables-matrix table table-bordered table-striped"><thead><tr><th>Param</th><th>Type</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>jqmPanelContainer <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-expression">expression</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpanelcontainer-page"><p>Assignable angular expression to data-bind the panel&#39;s open state to.
This is either <code>left</code> (show left panel), <code>right</code> (show right panel) or null.</p>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<h2 id="example">Example</h2>
<div class="example"><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpanelcontainer-page"><h4 id="example_source">Source</h4>
<div source-edit="jqm" source-edit-deps="angular.js" source-edit-html="index.html-8" source-edit-css="" source-edit-js="" source-edit-json="" source-edit-unit="" source-edit-scenario=""></div>
<div class="tabbable"><div class="tab-pane" title="index.html">
<pre class="prettyprint linenums" ng-set-text="index.html-8" ng-html-wrap-loaded="jqm angular.js"></pre>
<script type="text/ng-template" id="index.html-8">
 <div ng-init="state={}"></div>
 <div jqm-panel-container="state.openPanel" style="height:300px;overflow:hidden">
  <div jqm-panel position="left">
    Hello, left panel!
  </div>
  <div jqm-panel position="right" display="overlay">
   Hello, right panel!
  </div>
  <div style="background: white">
     Opened panel: {{state.openPanel}}
     <button ng-click="state.openPanel='left'">Open left</button>
     <button ng-click="state.openPanel='right'">Open right</button>
  </div>
 </div>
</script>
</div>
